  "profile": {
    "id": "u03_rohan",
    "user_name": "Rohan",
    "profession": "Bank PO aspirant",
    "mother_tongue": "Bengali",
    "interests": "Football, Bengali cinema, photography",
    "engagement": "chatty",
    "english_level": "A2",
    "personality": "enthusiastic, makes more grammar slips, talks about football a lot"
  },
  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, I hope your camera is fixed soon. What kind of photography do you enjoy most? Maybe we can talk about some good shots you've taken."
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I like taking photos of nature and football matches. Last week, I click some picture of my local team. The light was good, but my phone camera not so great. Do you like photography?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, I like photography too. You said 'click some picture' — we say 'take some pictures'. Good try! What team did you photograph?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "My local football team, they play in our town league. I try to capture the action, like when the player run fast or score a goal. Oh, and sometimes I take photo of the crowd too. They are very passionate! Do you watch football?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, that sounds fun! You said 'photo' — we say 'photos' when talking about more than one. I enjoy watching football too. Which team do you like?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I like the local team, Mohun Bagan Fans Club. They are not professional, but they play with lot of passion. I also follow some Indian Super League team, like Mumbai City. The matches are so exciting! Do you follow any team?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, 'with lot of passion' — we say 'with a lot of passion'. Small fix! I follow the Indian Super League too. Do you watch the matches live or on TV?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I watch matches mostly on TV, but if my team play near me, I try go live. The crowd is so energetic! Last weekend I see a match in Kolkata, the stadium was full! Do you like watch live matches?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, 'see a match' — we say 'watch a match'. Small tweak! I enjoy live matches too. Was it a good game?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yes, it was a good game! My team, Mohun Bagan Fans Club, win 3-2. The last goal was amazing, I almost jump from my seat! I take lot of photo that day, but my phone camera still need improve. Was there any good match you watch live?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, 'take lot of photo' — we say 'take a lot of photos'. You did great! I once watched a Mumbai City match live — very exciting! What’s your favorite part of football?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "My favorite part is when the player score last minute goal — it's so thrilling! I also love the way the crowd sing and cheer. It make me feel alive! Do you enjoy that moment too?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, 'It make me feel' — we say 'it makes me feel'. Small fix! I love that too — the energy is amazing. Do you sing along with the crowd?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yes, I try to sing along! Not very well, but I give it my best shot. Sometimes I even make up small song in Bengali. It’s fun! I think I better go now — need to revise for bank exam. Talk to you soon!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, 'I think I better go' — we say 'I think I’d better go'. Take care, and good luck with your revision! Talk soon."
    }
  ],
